{"tid":852656,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"【曼谷遊客死】水門巿場附近爆槍擊 多人中流彈2遊客死5傷","createTime":"2018-10-08T04:19:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-08T05:28:50.000Z","uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"fb95f2bc2a6c37f5f165198fb56066c390c7467f","tid":852656,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:19:40.000Z","msg":"大家快 d 改去台灣,日本,北韓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181008/58769241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58769241&d=GnYOVBWD5ThRqoI9%2BJHumWxr1Wzy5cvmMlqj7aCMUDs%3D&h=1615801c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181008%2F58769241&h=c7b368d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20181008/58769241</a><br />\n<br />\n【更新內容】<br />\n泰國曼谷巿中心遊客常到的水門亭閣購物中心（Watergate Pavillion Mall）附近爆發槍擊案，子彈橫飛期間傷及無辜遊客，兩遊客中彈死亡，另外5人受傷，其中一名死者<span style=\"color: red;\">當時正在現場等待酒店穿梭巴士。</span><br />\n案發在位處曼谷機場鐵路終點站的拍耶泰（PhayaThai），一班遊客昨夜剛吃完晚餐在停車場等車回酒店期間附近爆發槍戰，流彈導致2名泰國人、2名印度遊客及1名老撾遊客中槍，他們全部送到附近的醫院急救，一名42歲印度遊客及老撾遊客搶救不治。<br />\n警方指兩幫人因打桌球起爭執，在停車場爆發打鬥開槍觸發事件，警方也指情況相當罕見，「很少見，我被派往這個警區後從未見過這種事」。當局事發後調查商場內的閉路電視，並追捕涉事人士。<br />\n<br />\n即係仲未拉到人?!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ac68a7a81b88abb4c9647a443e3bbf10eed34e3","tid":852656,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-08T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"泰國 baht 應該急跌啦.....<br />\n打死旅遊業"},{"pid":"2926442a1bddc554c5d46af4c